{"tid":2201393,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"你地喺隧道揸車會唔會開低燈？","createTime":"2020-09-13T18:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T19:18:15.000Z","uid":155763,"like":5,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"fd158354a15cef8ffef52571379a4096e8d31d34","tid":2201393,"uid":155763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"呢排夜咗返屋企，揸車經過紅隧單管雙行，成日見到好多私家車都照開大燈，殘到對面線嘅我。唔知你哋平時喺呢個情況喺隧道揸車會唔會開低燈呢？<br />\n<br />\n有樣嘢我留意到嘅係職業司機特別係的士佬反而會開低燈。雖然平時啲職業司機喺路面揸車好危險，但係起碼佢哋喺呢個情況會顧及對面線司機嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dd635c4f99782b46ae5ac46da06ef201f370ba","tid":2201393,"uid":954,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:31:35.000Z","msg":"有幾多車開大燈呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591cfd0da53dd22e59bf33a7492133fd2cc0e2ba","tid":2201393,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"唔會 因為我唔係司機"},{"pid":"319cde69b969c2b6106b06598bbf13e90035f6a8","tid":2201393,"uid":58618,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:42:53.000Z","msg":"除左大雨到睇唔到前面 唔係不嬲用低燈架咩"},{"pid":"1d6b2ea1e84ff9ca750a49760845ecb7324c86ee","tid":2201393,"uid":27970,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:44:15.000Z","msg":"開高燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0d949a92aff63282c68af650a5ddaf034cd867","tid":2201393,"uid":111105,"like":36,"dislike":4,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:47:12.000Z","msg":"開頭燈預設唔係低燈咩，高燈要特登轉㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a881f05fa7e91cf185cbd1f517f01d02e47913","tid":2201393,"uid":50419,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d7dd635c4f99782b46ae5ac46da06ef201f370ba","tid":2201393,"uid":